{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f49bd43ed","title":"为什么肿病继续上升","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2569ce5bfa","index":0,"year":1959,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"5f49bd43ed"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"76f59e5fe2","name":"《宣教动态》"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"231ce594a1","type":"title","text":"为什么肿病继续上升","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"a1658db312","type":"authors","text":"《宣教动态》","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"c0d8b9f8c9","type":"paragraph","text":"据卫生部报告，入春以来，肿病又有上升趋势，涉及面也较广。从今年一月到目前，在山东、河南、江苏等十一个省、自治区共发生肿病一百零五万五千余人，死亡六千七百余人。其中以山东省最为严重，一月至四月十四日发生肿病病人七十七万九千余人，死亡六百一十八人，仅四月一日至十日一旬中即发生肿病病人十七万三千余人。其次是河南省，从一月到四月二十日发生肿病十五万三千余人，死亡二千余人。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"24fb7fed08","type":"paragraph","text":"肿病发生的原因，据各地报告有以下几点：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"b216cfbc6e","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，口粮较紧。也有个别地区群众误以为吃盐可以增加力气，每天吃盐一两以上（正常日需三钱），因吃盐过多，引起代谢障碍发生浮肿。也有吃野菜而引起的过敏反应。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"ea06fcccb8","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，食品种类单调，长时间未能谓节，脂肪、蛋白质严重缺乏或不平衡。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"b521f140f6","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，去年患过肿病，未根治，今年复发（河南省较多）。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"d46bfda7c3","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，原患有慢性病（如钩虫病等）、贫血、身体虚弱、年龄大、胃肠不好。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"},{"id":"d9ca1de506","type":"paragraph","text":"现各地都在采取紧急措施防治。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed"}],"page":{"id":"a16f92a111","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5f49bd43ed","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}